articles.title: FGR4 Eurofighter Typhoons ‘Thunder’ Over Yemen As US, UK Launch Deadly Strikes On Houthi Rebels - EurAsian Times
articles.description: Four RAF Typhoon FGR4s, backed by a Voyager air refueling tanker, used Paveway IV-guided bombs to conduct precision strikes on Houthi rebels. A number of buildings involved in drone operations were targeted by RAF jets, according to UK MoD. The other location…
